data.details:
Me and My Gal- Entrepreneur- CSA
Grades: 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, 11, 12

Do you dream of one day becoming a woman business owner? Grab your favorite gal, mom, grandma, troop leader, or another favorite lady, and get your creative juices flowing! Fantastic ideas and creative inventions are only half the game. Figure out if people would buy your invention or use your idea, and put your plan into action. Fun patch included.

*This event is for 2016 registered Girl Scouts.
* For safety and supervision reasons, troops and individuals are not permitted to bring non-Girl Scouts or siblings.
*Girl/adult ratios must be followed and adults are expected to stay on the premises during the event.

$15/girl, $10/adult
Contact: Brittany McCallister 904.389.3071
